flowRoot.flowPara: Patients that takes their drugs tend to be remote controlled. The algorithm that controles them seems to learn and adapt the places where i try to hide so that i can work without beeing bugged.

In Königsfelden they always know where the patients are, otherwise they could not bug me permanently. Maybe eye1 card or maybe something like implanted RFID and the uplink eg. the fire alarm system. Unfortunately tempering with the fire alarm system would be a really really bad idea, but maybe we could order the same system as they have here in Königsfelden to temper with... worst case it's not a default system and has unknown addons, in that case i guess in the Workshop near the railways, they maybe have some unused parts...
